Package: HOIF
Type: Package
Title: Higher Order Influence Function Estimators for Average Treatment Effects
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Xingyu", "Chen", 
                  email = "xingyuchen0714@sjtu.edu.cn",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0008-0823-4406"))
Description: Implements Higher Order Influence Function (HOIF) estimators for
    Average Treatment Effect (ATE) estimation. The package provides functions
    to compute HOIF estimators using U-statistics with various basis 
    transformations (B-splines, Fourier) and supports cross-fitting for
    improved finite-sample performance. The core U-statistic computation
    leverages Python's u-stats package via reticulate.
